rows.label: bf09090100_0010
rows.name:
What's with this guy? Is he planning to
summon all the Divine Beasts here?

rows.label: bf09090100_0020
rows.name: Yoshitsune! Benkei!

rows.label: bf09090100_0030
rows.name: Sata.

rows.label: bf09090100_0040
rows.name:
Go!
Go keep Shin and Metsu safe!

rows.label: bf09090100_0050
rows.name: What is this all of a sudden?

rows.label: bf09090100_0060
rows.name: We should prepare for the worst-case scenario.

rows.label: bf09090100_0070
rows.name:
What about Acedia? They're gathering Divine Beasts
from around the world...

rows.label: bf09090100_0080
rows.name: I'll take care of it.

rows.label: bf09090100_0090
rows.name:
Take care of it... alone?
That's impossible!

rows.label: bf09090100_0100
rows.name:
It's fine.
I built this thing in the first place, you know?

rows.label: bf09090100_0110
rows.name:
I can control everything from here
And also...

rows.label: bf09090100_0120
rows.name: I have a dependable ally with me.

rows.label: bf09090100_0130
rows.name: Sata...

rows.label: bf09090100_0140
rows.name: I'm counting on you, in my stead..

rows.label: bf09090100_0150
rows.name: [ML:Dash ]Understood

rows.label: bf09090100_0155
rows.name: Benkei!

rows.label: bf09090100_0160
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]!

rows.label: bf09090100_0170
rows.name: Benkei!

rows.label: bf09090100_0180
rows.name: I love you.

rows.label: bf09090100_0190
rows.name: You're being creepy, Sata.

rows.label: bf09090100_0200
rows.name:
I'll beat you up later
so don't you dare die.

rows.label: bf09090100_0210
rows.name: That[ML:Dash ] doesn't sound bad.
